data.description: Welcome home!   This amazing home is located in Poinciana within a couple miles of Publix, Walmart, banks, restaurants, and many more stores. This property includes modern finishes such as stainless steel appliances.This wonderful house has 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 of the rooms have a walk-in closet, pantry, a living room and also a large patio. two car Garage. Home 2021
